{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm all there, but I've got a big bump on my head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it hurts, very tender.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stagger about.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They did-- by this time the Germans didn't even bother to count us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no appell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Suddenly in the dusk, I hear in German the prisoners calling, [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I run towards where they are calling, and I come to some Polish prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I knew it couldn't be Leo because Leo is in Germany somewhere in Saxony.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So, you know, and I am south of the Danube in Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I knew the difference between Germany and Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It seemed inconceivable to me that it was Leo, but his name is being called.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Leo Honigwachs comes up and it's a stranger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they're all getting ready to run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I say to this Leo Honigwachs, where are you from, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My name is Honigwachs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we always knew that Honigwachs is such a rare name we have to be related.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he named some Polish city, which is meaningless to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And now I know the geography very well because I've done some studies because of this genealogy work that I do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But even now people say to me names of shtetls which I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, he refuses to take me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, you can't run and you'll, you'll hold us up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not taking you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that's like a few weeks before the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've never discovered this Leo Honigwachs, although I have found another Leo Honigwachs in Canada who is my fifth cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's another story about genealogy.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
